annotationA: U6 snRNA-associated Sm-like protein LSm2; Binds specifically to the 3'-terminal U-tract of U6 snRNA
annotationB: Decapping protein 2, isoform E; Protein binding; RNA binding; manganese ion binding; m7G(5')pppN diphosphatase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: nuclear-transcribed mRNA catabolic process; regulation of cytoplasmic mRNA processing body assembly; deadenylation-dependent decapping of nuclear-transcribed mRNA; gene silencing by miRNA
